2D-Game-Optimization
│
├── assets/                 # Folder for any example assets (e.g., sprites, sounds)
├── docs/                   # Documentation for contributors and users
├── src/                    # Core optimization tools and scripts
│   ├── collision.js        # Collision detection utilities (bounding box, etc.)
│   ├── gameLoop.js         # Optimized game loop using requestAnimationFrame
│   ├── imageLoader.js      # Preload images and assets efficiently
│   ├── objectPool.js       # Object pooling for efficient resource management
│   ├── performance.js      # General performance optimization utilities
│   └── utils.js            # Utility functions for general tasks (e.g., math, input)
├── examples/               # Example games demonstrating optimization techniques
│   └── basicGame.html      # A simple HTML5 game using the optimizations
├── .gitignore              # To ignore unnecessary files
├── LICENSE                 # License file (e.g., MIT)
└── README.md               # Information about the repository
